I checked out the spacedock website, trying to find mods... I noticed there is a search-bar at the top, so I just tried typing in Mechjeb then CKAN, and a few others.. It seems to show every single mod EXCEPT the one I typed in.. does anyone actually know how to navigate this mod "suppository"   lol
  (edit) nevermind, I checked out the overly complicated advanced search.l everything is fine now. lol
